Rating, 5 stars,  · January 2023,  · Stayed a few nights
rating_comment: While the place was very beautiful and exactly the same as described the host was even better! Literally went out of her way to help us and genuinely appreciate her for that! Wonderful person she is and yes, this is definitely one of those rare hassle free Airbnbs in Dhaka that won’t rip off guests staying by false advertising.
